Acting Governor of the Khabarovsk Territory Mikhail Degtyarev on Sunday, July 26, during a meeting with residents of Sovetskaya Gavan, was surprised that the region buys Sakhalin gas, produced by the American company Exxon Neftegas, for dollars.
